## Development

A Nix shell is provided for development:

```sh
nix develop
```

Build to run tests:

```sh
nix build
```

## Build and Publish

Build the source distribution:

```sh
python -m build --sdist --wheel
```

Check the distribution(s):

```sh
twine check dist/*
```

Upload the distribution:

```sh
twine upload -s dist/*
```

